data.description: Luxury meets livability with this open concept beautifully crafted condominium facing the south ocean coast. Boasting three bedrooms, two bathrooms and two covered parking spaces for you and your Ohana or guests. Guest parking open as well. Right in the heart of town which allows you to access all Oahu has to offer and only steps from your home. Moana Pacific is known for its recreation deck which hosts two tennis courts, putting green, swimming pool, multiple BBQ's and even a theater room for all to enjoy.
data.whatILove: Situated on the 29th floor, experience incredible 180 degree views spanning from the ocean, downtown Honolulu skyline to the picturesque lush green mountain range all viewable by 19 floor to ceiling glass windows.
